NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Singleton - Singleton to context

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst qw[Singleton];

        # Retrieve a instance of context
        my $c = MyApp->instance;
        my $c = MyApp->context;

DESCRIPTION
    Singleton to context.

SEE ALSO
    Catalyst.

